  - llm
  - tool-use
  - orchestration
abstract: >-
  Testudo is a dockerised agent runtime that runs an entire agent workflow end-to-end
  inside a hardened container, with declarative per-workflow permissioning, full audit
  logging, and rollback semantics. It embeds a lightweight workflow orchestrator so the
  container is the deployment unit ("the agent"), and exposes a host-side adapter so
  Hillstar Orchestrator can invoke a Testudo container as a single DAG step.
